    "gotchas": [
        "Prisma 7+ requires @prisma/adapter-libsql for SQLite",
        "TailwindCSS v4 uses @import 'tailwindcss' - Google Fonts must use next/font instead of @import url()",
        "TailwindCSS v4 layer specificity: base styles (h1-h6) must be wrapped in @layer base to allow utility overrides",
        "ZodError uses .issues not .errors (Zod v3+)",
        "Fields with _en suffix are for English i18n content",
        "ContentSection uses entityType + entityId pattern for polymorphic relations",
        "Button asChild prop requires @radix-ui/react-slot",
        "Gallery grid must be 2x4 (grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4) per UI_DESIGN.md §9",
        "Homepage section order must follow UI_DESIGN.md §9 exactly",
        "NewsCard must wrap entire article in Link for full clickability",
        "Use Lucide icons (not emojis) per UI/UX pro-max workflow",
        "Featured badge and Star icon use blue color (not amber) per user preference",
        "Course pages use GraduationCap icon as placeholder for missing thumbnails",
        "Ghost button variant text color (slate-700) overrides text-white utility on dark backgrounds due to same-layer specificity - use !text-white !bg-transparent",
        "Locale-specific images use separate FK columns (featuredImageId_en, avatarId_en, logoId_en) with own Media relations — admin UI switches fields based on URL locale param",
        "Media scan route must check BOTH vi and _en FK fields to avoid falsely flagging EN images as unused",
        "Admin edit pages at /admin/[locale]/... show locale-specific fields (name_en, content_en, avatar_en etc.) when locale=en, shared fields (isActive, sortOrder etc.) only in vi mode",
        "Sticky Header requires 0 padding on <main> top to avoid whitespace gaps"
    ],
